Code: EXEC SQL SELECT t1.NRPARCEL, t1.ocorhist, t1.dacparc, t1.num_apolice, t1.nrendos, t2.tipo_endosso FROM seguros.v1parcela t1, seguros.v1parcela t2 WHERE t1.num_apolice = :NUM_APOLICE AND t1.nrendos = :NRENDOS AND t1.situacao = '0' AND t1.num_apolice = t2.num_apolice AND t1.nrendos = t2.nrendos ORDER BY 1 END SQL
